when swapping a docker container from debian to alpine, i got `spawn-fcgi: child exited with: 2` while trying to spawn-fcgi

this is because the Alpine `fcgiwrap` package puts the binary in `/usr/bin/fcgiwrap`


https://unix.stackexchange.com/questions/635674/problem-with-default-fcgiwrap-socket-access-rights-and-nginx-alpine-linux

